info.name: Provincie Zeeland Bulk Test
info.description:
The API-services can be divided into four parts; objectId, files, export and webhook

**ObjectId**

- CreateId
    

**Files**

- GetFileUrl
    
- GetFileUrlByAddtionalId
    
- GetFileMetadata
    
- CreateFile
    
- CreateLargeFile
    
- UpdateFileMetadata
    
- UpdateFileContent
    
- UpdateLargeFileContent
    
- UpdateFileName
    

**Export**

- SynchroniseNewDocuments
    
- SynchroniseUpdatedDocuments
    
- SynchroniseDeletedDocuments
    

**Webhook**

- CreateWebhook
    
- HandleSharePointNotification
    
- HandleDropOffNotification
    

See documentation for each folder for more information about the tests.

request.description: Create file by content and metadata

Synchronise new documents

- Upload content and metadata to storage container
    
- Send new file to callback
    

The created file in the previous step must be synchronised.

Get file url by objectId or additionalObjectId

The url to the created file in step one must be returned.

body.raw: ""

request.description:
Update content for file by objectId

The content from the created file in step four must be updated.

Synchronise updated documents

- Update content and metadata in storage container
- Send updated file to callback
    

The updated file created in step four must be synchronised.

Synchronise deleted documents

- Delete content and metadata from storage container
    
- Send deleted file to callback
    

Manually action: delete a file to synchronise

item.description:
Run a test

Pick one option and run the test: - Option 1 - Open the folder (Bulk Test) - Klik op **Run** - Option 2 - Open new runner tab CTRL+SHIFT+R - Add all the requests from the folder (Bulk test) - Click on **Run** Provincie Zeeland Bulk Test Increase the number of iterations to run mutliple tests. Please note that you are authenticated in **Authorization**.

More information

SynchroniseNewDocuments needs an extra manual test: Is the file present in the Blob Container content in Azure. SynchronizeUpdatedDocuments needs an extra manual test: Does the file in the Blob Container content in Azure has the latest version. SynchronizeDeletedDocuments will only work when a file is deleted before running.

item.description:
Run a test

Pick one option and run the test: - Option 1 - Open the folder (LocationMapping Test) - Klik op **Run** - Option 2 - Open new runner tab CTRL+SHIFT+R - Add all the requests from the folder (LocationMapping Test) - Click on **Run** Provincie Zeeland Bulk Test Increase the number of iterations to run mutliple tests. Please note that you are authenticated in **Authorization**.

More information

SynchroniseNewDocuments needs an extra manual test: Is the file present in the Blob Container content in Azure. SynchronizeUpdatedDocuments needs an extra manual test: Does the file in the Blob Container content in Azure has the latest version. SynchronizeDeletedDocuments will only work when a file is deleted before running.
